Live Material Pricing: An API integration (like Home Depot or Lowe's) that updates their "Material Cost" field based on current local zip code prices.This must be free, or nearly free for me as well as the consumer. 
Auto Calculate Materials: Based on the trade selected, the ability to auto calculate and recommend certain components and/or materials costs based on data input in the scope of work. EG - Fence installer lists 185’ of 6’ Steel fencing, four 42” gates, and one 92” double gate - the app should be able to calculate how many posts, how many fencing panels, how many gates, how much concrete and auto fill those entries. This should be possible for all trades, but we’ll pick one to start with (likely landscaping for fencing) 
